              <tr><td><strong>Click share (BrightLocal)</strong></td><td>35% of local clicks</td><td>42% of local clicks</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Best query type</strong></td><td class="cell-yes">Informational + transactional</td><td>Transactional + near-me</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Stability</strong></td><td class="cell-yes">High — less location-dependent</td><td class="cell-meh">Medium — shifts with searcher location</td></tr>
            </tbody>
