            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Local organic results derive from your website, not your Google Business Profile. A strong local landing page and local keyword targeting can rank in local organic results even without a GBP listing. However, an optimized GBP indirectly supports organic rankings through prominence signals.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
